in: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-right-color: rgb(250, 208, 21); border-bottom-color: transparent !important; border-top-width: 1em !important; border-right-width: 0.5em; border-bottom-width: 1em !important; border-top-style: solid !important; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid !important; display: inline-block; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; height: 2em; color: rgb(7, 7, 7); line-height: 2em; vertical-align: top; display: inline-block; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgba(211, 207, 206, 0.117647);\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\">移动光通信设备</strong></p></span><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important; border-left-color: rgb(250, 208, 21); border-top-width: 1em !important; border-bottom-width: 1em !important; border-left-width: 0.5em; border-top-style: solid !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-left-style: solid; display: inline-block; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;随着对空间通信带宽的要求越来越高，现有的无线电和微波通信方式已经不能满足其要求，而空间光通信技术是很好的解决方案。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"/></p></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(7, 7, 7); line-height: 1.8; letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(250, 208, 21); font-size: 18px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;移动光通信</span></strong>也称无线激光通信或自由空间光通信（FSO）它是以激光作为载波实现高速移动通信的一种空间通信方式。</p></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(7, 7, 7); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;那么移动光通信都能做些啥呢？<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;简单地说就是光纤通信、移动通信做不到的，我们都能做到！霸不霸气~<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"/></p></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(7, 7, 7); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;移动光通信结合了光纤通信和移动无线通信的优点，同时具有光纤通信的<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(250, 208, 21); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\">高带宽</span>和移动通信<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(250, 208, 21); -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\">无线便捷</span>的优点。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\">可以实现：</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天-空-地一体化高速通信网；</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;卫星、飞机、飞艇、船、车等移动平台之间的高速通信。</span></p></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-