100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; color: rgb(7, 7, 7);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">研制出<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(246, 43, 9);\">国内首台</span></strong>WDM激光通信机系统，完成了2.5Gbps速率16km距离空间激光通信实验。</p></section></section></section></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '2018-01-15 01:13:06.461368', '2018-02-22 11:49:07.752496', '12', '1', '11', 'story/images/2018/01/11.jpg');
INSERT INTO `oce_story` VALUES ('24', '高速机载激光通信工程机', 'gao-su-ji-zai-ji-guang-tong-xin-gong-cheng-ji', '<p>2014年12月,研制出高速机载激光通信工程样机，交付用户。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/media/story/images/13_20180115011612_864.jpg\" alt=\"13.jpg\" width=\"367\" height=\"330\" style=\"width: 367px; height: 330px;\"/></p><section class=\"\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(7, 7, 7);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"text-align: left;\"/></p></section></section></section><p><br style=\"text-align: left;\"/></p>', '3', '2018-01-15 01:16:46.294774', '2018-02-22 18:27:28.719029', '45', '1', '11', 'story/images/2018/01/13.jpg');
INSERT INTO `oce_story` VALUES ('25', '天宫二号星地激光通信实验圆满成功', 'tian-gong-er-hao-xing-di-ji-guang-tong-xin-shi-yan-yuan-man-cheng-gong', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天宫二号激光通信载荷以武汉大学、武汉六博光电技术有限责任公司共同研制完成，于2016年9月15日搭载天宫二号发射升空。天宫二号10月在完成载人交会对接等任务以后，2016年11月开始天地激光通信测试，2016年12月成功地与新疆南山光学地面接收机进行了多次高速激光通信试验，将天宫二号上多个科学载荷业务数据以1.6Gbps速率进行高质量下传。天宫二号在我国首次实现超Gbps速率的天地业务数据传输试验，创下我国卫星业务通信速率的新纪录。高速激光通信链路的建立，有效缓解了传统微波通信带宽不足的瓶颈问题，为我国后续空间站更高容量数据传输打下了坚实的基础。天宫二号激光通信端机目前运转正常，各项指标达到了国际先进水平。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 68, 41); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span>天宫二号激光通信端机产品构成如图1所示，包括综合控制单元、激光通信控制电路主板与备板、光复用器（DWDM）单元、光功率放大（EDFA）单元、准直光学单元，全部按照航天要求研制。另外还专门研制了高性能地面通信接收机，构成天地高速激光通信回路。图2给出了2016年12月22日星地高速激光通信数据接收结果，图3给出了接收伽玛暴探测器数据的反演结果。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"33.jpg\" src=\"http://wh-fso.com/media/story/images/33_20180124180637_304.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">图1 天宫二号激光通信端机构成图</span></p><p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><img alt=\"22.jpg\" src=\"http://wh-fso.com/media/story/images/22_20180124180525_398.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">图2 2016年12月22日 星地高速激光通信实验结果</span></p><p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img style=\"WIDTH: 599px; HEIGHT: 245px\" alt=\"11.png\" src=\"http://wh-fso.com/media/story/images/11_20180124180237_900.png\" width=\"1465\" height=\"617\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">图3 2016年12月22日下传的伽玛暴探测器数据的反演结果</span></p><p><br style=\"text-align: left;\"/></p>', '3', '2018-01-24 18:12:18.126580', '2018-03-17 14:40:00.255697', '65', '1', '14', 'story/images/2018/01/33.jpg');
INSERT INTO `oce_story` VALUES ('26', '轻便式激光通信机', 'qing-bian-shi-ji-guang-tong-xin-ji', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">设备型号：</span>LB-125M15</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/media/story/images/LB-125M15_20180126193924_794.jpg\" alt=\"LB-125M15.jpg\" width=\"554\" height=\"474\" style=\"width: 554px; height: 474px;\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">产品功能</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">六博</span>1550<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">波长</span>125M<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">速率中距离便携式激光通信系统空间光通信机</span>.</p><p>a. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">信号激光输出、输入；</span></p><p>b. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">信标激光输出；</span></p><p>c. CCD<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">信号输入；</span></p><p>d. CCD<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">图像转</span>AV<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">视频接口输出；</span></p><p>e.<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">以太网口</span>1<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">和</span>2<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">可接摄像机做显示输入、也可以接互联网做外网输入，以太网口</span>3<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">和</span>4<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">可以做显示图像输出和网络接收端。；</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">主要技术参数：</span></p><p>1<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">）网络接口参数</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">工作模式：</span>10/100/1000Base-TX<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">，半双工</span>/<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">全双工</span>/<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">自协商</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">传输速率：</span>100Mbps</p><p>2<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">）光学指标</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">发光波长：</span>1550nm</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">发射速率：</span>125Mb/s</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">平均发送光功率：≥</span>-12dBm</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信模式：双向（全双工）；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信内容：视频、语音、数据、网络。</span></p><p>3<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">）其他参数</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">电源输入：</span>AC220V<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">±</span>10%</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">重量：</span>10kg<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">功耗：≤</span>60W<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '2018-01-26 19:40:39.916997', '2018-02-22 11:49:09.089760', '345', '1', '11', 'story/images/2018/01/LB-125M15.jpg');
INSERT INTO `oce_story` VALUES ('27', '便携式激光通信系统', 'bian-xi-shi-ji-guang-tong-xin-xi-tong', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">设备型号：</span>LB-100-15-1250M</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/media/story/images/LB-100-15-1250M_20180126195419_764.jpg\" alt=\"LB-100-15-1250M.jpg\" width=\"565\" height=\"782\" style=\"width: 565px; height: 782px;\"/></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\"><br/></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">产品功能</span></strong></p><p>100<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">口径</span>1550<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">波长</span>1.25G<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">速率中距离便携式激光通信系统</span>.</p><p>a. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">手动调节光学捕获，对准；</span></p><p>b. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">内置监测</span>CCD<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">，便于目标对准；</span></p><p>c. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">双波束发射；</span></p><p>d. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">快速机动架设，适合野外临时通信；</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">主要技术参数：</span></p><p>1<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">）发射性能指标</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信波长：</span>1530~1550nm</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">发射速率：</span>1.25Gb/s<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">信号发射光功率：</span>0.2W~1W<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信距离：</span>1km~2km<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信模式：双向（全双工）；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信内容：视频、语音、数据、网络。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">光学接收口径：</span>100mm<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">（收发一体）；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">接收视场：</span>8mrad<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">角度范围：方位：</span>360<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°</span>;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">俯仰：</span>+/-70<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">手调精度：</span>10urad<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">重量（不含三角架）：</span> 3kg<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">功耗：</span>20W<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '2018-01-26 19:55:40.352032', '2018-03-17 15:12:15.646537', '65', '1', '11', 'story/images/2018/01/LB-100-15-1250M.jpg');
INSERT INTO `oce_story` VALUES ('28', '大口径GPS辅助跟瞄激光通信系统', 'da-kou-jing-gpsfu-zhu-gen-miao-ji-guang-tong-xin-xi-tong', '<p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">设备型号：</span>LB-GA250-15-2500L</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/media/story/images/LB-GA250-15-2500L_20180127014931_595.jpg\" alt=\"LB-GA250-15-2500L.jpg\" width=\"411\" height=\"493\" style=\"width: 411px; height: 493px;\"/></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">产品功能</span></strong></p><p>GPS<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">辅助跟瞄</span>250<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">口径</span>1550<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">波长</span>2.5G<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">速率远距离空间激光通信系统。</span></p><p>a. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">高速空间激光通信；</span></p><p>b. GPS<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">辅助自动光学捕获，对准，跟踪（</span>APT((Acquisition,Pointing and Tracking)<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">，（捕获，对准，跟踪））；</span></p><p>c. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">有独立的供配电；</span></p><p>d. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">关键模块或单元工作状态监测；</span></p><p>e. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">终端支持</span>WDM<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">信道复用</span>/<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">解复用，可扩展到</span>5-10Gbps<span style=\"font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">速率；</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">主要技术参数：</span></p><p>1<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">）发射性能指标</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信波长：</span>1530~1550nm</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">发射速率：</span>2.5Gb/s<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">信号发射光功率：</span>0.2W~2W<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信距离：</span>1km~40km<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信模式：双向（全双工）；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信内容：视频、语音、数据、网络。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">重量：</span>30kg<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">功耗：</span>80W<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>2<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">）</span>ATP<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">性能指标</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">光学接收口径：</span>250mm<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">（收发一体）；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">接收视场：</span>6mrad<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">跟踪范围：方位：</span>360<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°</span>;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">俯仰：</span>+/-70<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">最大跟踪角速度：</span>20<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°</span>/s<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">最大跟踪角加速度：</span>30<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°</span>/s2<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">跟踪精度：</span>5urad<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">目标捕获：自动；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">目标捕获时间：</span>&lt;15s<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">目标重捕时间：</span>&lt;15s<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '2018-01-27 01:50:13.114101', '2018-03-17 15:12:34.057735', '57', '1', '11', 'story/images/2018/01/LB-GA250-15-2500L.jpg');
INSERT INTO `oce_story` VALUES ('29', '激光网桥', 'ji-guang-wang-qiao', '<p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">设备型号：</span>LB-JWQ100-15-2500M</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/media/story/images/LB-JWQ100-15-2500M_20180127015118_380.jpg\" alt=\"LB-JWQ100-15-2500M.jpg\" width=\"645\" height=\"324\" style=\"width: 645px; height: 324px;\"/></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">产品功能</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">无线激光网桥系统可以在两点或多点之间快速架设高速移动局域网，实现多点间手机、电话、电脑、视频等数据的宽带接入和互通。如果没有公网，可以实现多点局域网内手机、电话、电脑、视频等数据的互通。</span></p><p>a. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">手动调节光学捕获，对准；</span></p><p>b. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">内置监测</span>CCD<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">，便于目标对准；</span></p><p>c. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">双波束发射；</span></p><p>d. <span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">快速机动架设，适合野外临时通信；</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">主要技术参数：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信波长：</span>1530~1550nm</p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">发射速率：</span>2.5Gb/s<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">信号发射光功率：</span>0.2W~1W<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信距离：</span>1km~2km<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信模式：双向（全双工）；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">通信内容：视频、语音、数据、网络；</span></p><p>wifi<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">带宽：</span>100M<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">光学接收口径：</span>100mm<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">（收发一体）；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">接收视场：</span>8mrad<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">角度范围：方位：</span>360<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°</span>;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">俯仰：</span>+/-70<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">°；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">手调精度：</span>10urad<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">重量（不含三角架）：</span> 2kg<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">功耗：</span>20W<span style=\"font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif\">。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '3', '2018-01-27 01:51:38.039497', '2018-03-17 14:19:58.792000', '80', '1', '11', 'story/images/2018/01/LB-JWQ100-15-2500M.jpg');
